params.description: Required. The resource name for the related account group in the format projects/{project}/relatedaccountgroups/{relatedaccountgroup}.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of accounts to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 50 accounts will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.
